| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1270 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d691eb3a-b95c-5c0b-a2fc-00527d4f44cd"
